---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 115
By: Abu Sa'id ibn Abi ‘l-Khayr
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Consummation of Desire
  - Sacrifice-Death=Death=‘Die Before Ye Die’
---
Love that One Who, when you shall cease to be, will not Himself cease to be,
that you may become one who will never cease to be.
